Asif n Sibaw ?
Walaɣ itri tameddit n wass, ziɣmani d asatilit.
Imseɣti n tmaziɣt mazal ur t-nesɛi ara.
N wi k-ilan a mmi ?
N wi kem-ilan a taqcict ?
N wi ken-ilan ay arrac ?
N wi kent-ilan a ticennayin tibaḥanin ?
Tafat twala aggur, yusem fell-as.
Iseɣta tuccḍiwin s tiyeḍ.
Waki d ccɣel-inu nekk, kunemti ɛassemt aqaẓẓal-nni.
Asif n Buɣni akked Wasif n Deḥmun ad čcaren abaraj amaynut n Ttlata.
Ur qqar-iyi-d ara yemmut Bakli !
Melmi i d-yeḥmel wasif n Nnil abrid aneggaru ?
Asif n Nnil yekka-d seg Ugelmim n Victoria, yettawi ɣer Yilel Agrakal.
Saɛid iwennet taẓrigt-iw di facebook, yerna iḥemmel-itt.
Asif n Cakur yezga-d gar Tfuɣalt d Wat Reḥmun.
Targa tettili di lexla, ma d aḍref xeddment di tmazirt neɣ aɛerqub.
Aḥebbas n uzemmur yezmer ad yili aḍref.
Nekkni nectaq aman, nihni ttserriḥen-asen ɣer wasif.
Tɣelli-d tiqqit seg ssqef, tenjer targa.
Timeddelwit d tiqqit-nni i d-iɣellin seg uqermud mi ara yili ugeffur.
Sefti amyag ḥedded ɣer yizri akked umqim nihni.
Tabulɣarit temgarad ɣef teqbaylit.
Aqerquc tḍemɛeḍ deg yimi n taɣaṭ, yebmeɛ.
Imeṭṭawen nejren targa ɣef umayeg-is.
Yenna-yas : Berka imeṭṭi !
Tenna-yas : Ttruɣ ɣef tayri-yinu iruḥen ; yehwa-yi !
Yenna-yas : Susem tura ; tameddit ttru deg uxxam, tmeǧǧdeḍ ard teɛyuḍ.
Win yekkren ar wayeḍ yini-as "kečč d bu truggza !"
Sexrebceɣ akk afus-iw s ustilu azeggaɣ.
Weccmeɣ yiwen n yigider deg yiɣil-iw ayeffus.
Aselmad n tmaziɣt ma ur yettaru akken ilaq, amek ara d-ffɣen yinelmaden-is ?
Asif n Yesser yettawi ɣer lebḥer.
At Wasif seddaw udrar, i as-yenna Wakli Yeḥyaten.
Targa Uzemmur d amkan anda tettwabna tesdawit n Bgayet.
Tiregwa n Lewnis jemɛent-d ayen yecna di temẓi-s.
